history.content:
Dear Students,

Due to the many changes that have occurred lately, we've decided to extend the EECS Honors Program Application deadline to next Wednesday 4/8 at 4pm. 
Please visit the EECS Honors Program page to find more information and the application form. 
Please feel free to contact me at mejiavalencia@eecs.berkeley.edu if you have any questions.
Best,
Andrea
